fields.title: abandon ship; a family game, no. 2003-2
fields.history_note: Game represents a capsized ship where the players must acquire food, water and passengers to survive and ultimately to win.
fields.production_note: Ideal toy Co. Ltd under licence from the Ideal Toy Corp.
fields.historical_context_note:
Rewards: gaining equipment and passengers
Forfeits: losing equipment and passengers
No. of Players: 2 to 4
Equipment required: dice, markers in the shape of ship's officers, equipment in the shape of food and water; cards depicting passengers, lifeboats, adventure cards

Rules:
see copies of the rules in the games folders.

Rules placement: booklet
